From 02bb63d1a59341032b8e7e4021e18d044bdb1786 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andy Yan <andy.yan@rock-chips.com>
Date: Thu, 3 Jul 2025 20:49:52 +0800
Subject: drm/bridge: Make dp/hdmi_audio_* callback keep the same paramter
 order with get_modes
Git-commit: 02bb63d1a59341032b8e7e4021e18d044bdb1786
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
References: jsc#PED-13979 jsc#PED-14039 jsc#PED-14046 jsc#PED-14211 jsc#PED-14333 jsc#PED-14487 jsc#PED-14488 jsc#PED-14497 jsc#PED-14499 jsc#PED-15868

Make the dp/hdmi_audio_* callback maintain the same parameter order as
get_modes and edid_read: first the bridge, then the connector.

Signed-off-by: Andy Yan <andy.yan@rock-chips.com>
Reviewed-by: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@oss.qualcomm.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20250703125027.311109-2-andyshrk@163.com
[db: added the chunk to the cdn-dp driver]
Signed-off-by: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@oss.qualcomm.com>
Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>

